entry.title: Ukraine Launches Airstrikes on Russian-Held Targets
entry.content: Ukraine’s armed forces said its air force launched strikes on 11 Russian clusters of personnel and equipment over the past day as anticipation grew that Kyiv was on the brink of beginning a long-awaited offensive to regain lost territory.

entry.title: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer Charts a 'Pragmatic-Progressive' Course
entry.content: Democrats, led by Whitmer, are in control for the first time in 40 years. They have been fast-tracking their priorities, including expanded background checks for gun purchases and repeal of an abortion ban.
